fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.themes

Interface ITemplateList<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type contained in the list.

    public interface ITemplateList<V>
    Container for a sequence of values in a template dataset, with a fluent API for adding items.

    Invocations of add can be chained, to make it easier to write concise code.

    Thread-safety: implementations of this interface are not required to be safe for concurrent access. Therefore, processing should generally not be shared between multiple threads.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
    See Also:
    ITemplateData.createList(String, Object...)
